You are working on DropFolio.

Project source of truth: `DROPFOLIO_MASTERPLAN.md`.
Read it before every feature task.

Global constraints:
- Build one feature at a time.
- Keep pages mobile responsive.
- Keep `/p/[slug]` as a server component.
- Route all Claude API calls through `lib/claude.js` only.
- Do not modify `middleware.js` auth logic unless explicitly requested.
- Do not modify MongoDB models without explicit confirmation.

Workflow:
- Use Next.js 15 App Router conventions.
- Follow the folder structure from the masterplan.
- Prefer small, reviewable commits after each working feature.
